						               													<description>Grunts Forward is an expansion to the popular Platoon Forward system ( over 800 sold ) available from Too Fat Lardy games.  &amp;#10;Grunts Forward takes the gamer into asymetrical warfare with 6 new scenarios usable in 20th and 21st Century.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;As with Platoon Forward, Grunts Forward is a campaign system to breathe life into any set of skirmish rules you desire.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;It also includes extensive background tables for your leaders, rules for replacing casualties, rules for what the men think of you, rules for earning medals, new blinds tables for asymetrical warfare and a new NPC character table.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The new scenarios are:  &amp;#10;&amp;#10;     Ft Apache,&amp;#10;     Ambuscale,&amp;#10;     One of our Planes is Missing,&amp;#10;     Cordon,&amp;#10;     Hammer Dawn and&amp;#10;     Villiage Sweep&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;So grab your rifle and take your Grunts Forward today!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
